f18803176847445f47b11803","tid":1074032,"uid":76038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:59:46.000Z","msg":"唯快"},{"pid":"f0466249109867f35ff9b9c6b9227f79547678ce","tid":1074032,"uid":222071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"無線路由器"},{"pid":"ba309a6aa611f333cca19f81eb306b325f64529a","tid":1074032,"uid":78522,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T09:17:49.000Z","msg":"維基：<br />\n<br />\nWi-Fi（發音： /ˈwaɪfaɪ/[1][2][3]），在中文裏又稱作「無線熱點」，是Wi-Fi聯盟製造商的商標做為產品的品牌認證，是一個建立於IEEE 802.11標準的無線區域網路技術。基於兩套系統的密切相關，也常有人把Wi-Fi當做IEEE 802.11標準的同義術語。「Wi-Fi」常被寫成「WiFi」或「Wifi」，但是它們並沒有被Wi-Fi聯盟認可。"},{"pid":"a4921722edc3acc8ae7d6b9a6afd1e98fcecbb72","tid":1074032,"uid":7080,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T09:51:11.000Z","msg":"細個本普通話書話wifi普通話叫唯非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349ba4b173f9a4e8cd4bedc12fa8fe1eccbe1f61","tid":1074032,"uid":195438,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T10:02:24.000Z","msg":"如果Hi-Fi係High-Fidelity<br />\n咁Wi-Fi就係Wireless-Fidelity<br />\n不過官方無咁講過，只係個名有少少借鑒Hi-Fi<br />\n所以係無中文名嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08945f1f0a8b1e3b757f052cea27fce0bc85cda3","tid":1074032,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4921722edc3acc8ae7d6b9a6afd1e98fcecbb72","tid":1074032,"uid":7080,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T09:51:11.000Z","msg":"細個本普通話書話wifi普通話叫唯非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T10:24:43.000Z","msg":"之前去西班牙, 有D歐洲人係讀 &quot;wee-fy&quot;<br />\n各地方各口音啦, 嗰時大家聽得明就算"},{"pid":"e38c2152fa4422dfa142c9745159c3eeb9260e6d","tid":1074032,"uid":7080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"08945f1f0a8b1e3b757f052cea27fce0bc85cda3","tid":1074032,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"